{"tid":1334430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方在荃灣一個工廈單位檢獲烈性炸藥及燃燒彈","createTime":"2019-07-20T06:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T06:29:47.000Z","uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"239a7f71445d4a0c540665b6d1dd80cad43de90c","tid":1334430,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"警方在荃灣一座工廠大廈的單位發現懷疑爆炸品，包括烈性炸藥及燃燒彈，一批武器及鏹水等，拘捕一名27歲男子，他涉嫌無牌管有爆炸品。警方又表示，不排除會再有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，早前接報荃灣德士古道142號一幢工廠大廈有懷疑爆炸品，警方昨晚到場調查。爆炸品處理課人員昨晚帶同裝備到大廈天台進行引爆。有類似紙巾碎的碎屑散落在大廈附近的路面及警車上。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469377-20190720.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469377-20190720.htm&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=8ae00495\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469377-20190720.htm&h=8bc7bf65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469377-20190720.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n抹黑行動，正式啟動！"},{"pid":"2fe5101b4d372e41b786d5d8f5e380fa3ba9865d","tid":1334430,"uid":259700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4737e134a1d3d309f701fb507354b87dfb32c804","tid":1334430,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"【安已不】大陸有人呼籲河南黑工721做自殺式炸彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333902</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83c6d17cc1f4eda1f578d0e28a5e88715f0588d","tid":1334430,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fe5101b4d372e41b786d5d8f5e380fa3ba9865d","tid":1334430,"uid":259700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:29:47.